<cúú>Carpathian Gladiator Pit - Rules</c>


<cÈdd>1.   Once you have been beaten you will be ported to Challengers portal.  DO NOT go back into the duel. 

2.  No Excessive Spamming Anything!

3.  No Healing!  This includes Regeneration.

4.  DO NOT buff until countdown starts!
 
5.  DO NOT start fighting until countdown says "FIGHT!"

6.  FIGHT does NOT start until both players are standing in there       designated portals.

7.  Listen to the {DM} at all times or be Disqualified.

8.  When tournament is finished you will then receive a prize if awarded a      prize by the {DM}.

9.  DO NOT ask dm for any other prizes but what is offered to you.

10. NO COMPLAINING!

11. Have fun or dont participate.

12.  NO PVP OUTSIDE OF THE CAGE.  No using FEATS, SKILLS,        SPELLS outside of the cage..

13.  NO EXCESSIVE RUNNING TO AVOID COMBAT ONCE COMBAT BEGINS!  You can run for 6 Seconds max per sprint.  Do not abuse this evasive action to avoid death, or hope your opponents spell buffs disappear.  {DM} judges if excessive running occurs.  You will automatially forfeit your duel if you abuse this rule.

Cheers</c>
